>
{%- comment -%} End Yoast auto-disable. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- endif -%}
{%- comment -%}Auto-disabled. Yoast plugin is taking care of Meta Tags output.{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if disabled_by_yoast_seo -%}
<meta
